the particle will be slowed down,

84
00:05:10,907 --> 00:05:14,319
and therefore its Larmor radius
will become smaller,

85
00:05:14,534 --> 00:05:17,552
and then the particle
will continue to move.

86
00:05:17,900 --> 00:05:21,281
Will be slowed down, etc.

87
00:05:22,339 --> 00:05:26,999
The result is that
the particle's guiding center

88
00:05:27,746 --> 00:05:32,520
